HONKERSWORLDCANDYCLOWNS15.name: Honker's World: Candy Clowns #005
description: The Asylum is a high-rise mega club where
individuals can dance the night away and revel
in the chaos of Honker’s World. But beneath the
club's flashing lights and thumping music is a
hidden underground drug facility, where thousands
of demented Candy Clowns work tirelessly to
produce the latest and greatest designer drugs.
The clowns are notorious for their depraved and
hedonistic lifestyle, using their psychotic minds
to create drugs that are as insane as they are potent.
They revel in the creation of dangerous chemicals
and mind-altering compounds, mixing ingredients
with a sadistic glee that would chill the hearts
of even the bravest Herd Members.
